{"tid":1342783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 推牛屎佬加黑警落地獄","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:54:06.000Z","uid":150848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47b013e0287edc3cef0fe7ef76db5908c08bb2ac","tid":1342783,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"今日真係嬲到震，而家政府明顯想用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">牛屎佬</span></span>spin走<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警罪名</span></span>，但其實唔使理咁多，只要大大力推<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作就冇得輸</span></span>，唔可以比警黑做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑白兩面</span></span>，千其唔好比人覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警犬救咗我哋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大力推嘅point大致有呢幾個<br />\n<br />\n1.何妖同牛屎佬條片，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐警召集人公開警黑合作</span></span>，策劃攻擊示威者同<span style=\"color: red;\">途人</span><br />\n<br />\n2.警犬喺元朗站走佬條片，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方疑似同黑幫合作</span></span>，任由社團人士攻擊示威者和議員，並沒有立即派出增緩<br />\n<br />\n3.講真反黑揾CID都夠，一定冇藉口話啲人喺哂港島，呢個point 喺對家賴我哋之後一定要推<br />\n<br />\npoint:警方企圖把<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗執法不力罪名推卸示威者</span></span>，事實港島有xxxx名<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">精銳警察</span></span>，並向和平離去示威者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開槍和施放催淚彈</span></span>，仲有xxxxx名警察於各區<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未能盡責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想同各位講，唔好唔記得大佬<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仍然係中共</span></span>，係邊個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比錢吹雞牛屎佬同警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"badeb55783e61e31d2ddf4aba8634bdc4329dbd7","tid":1342783,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2cd509d641b9863a208c3b41e61591414b41375","tid":1342783,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"嬲到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6a43d9379beed69ea7fed6a1aad40263e6c8c6","tid":1342783,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到屋企嘅手足入黎!! 有地方落腳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e924e6ac69745d68c629becca971732dbf231b","tid":1342783,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T1